# local.properties is gitignored. The app no longer bakes the server URL or
# API token into the APK; both are configured at runtime via the in-app Setup
# screen. URLs are stored in app-private preferences; the API token is stored
# in the Keystore-backed secure store.
#
# This file only needs Android SDK paths, e.g.:
# sdk.dir=/Users/you/Library/Android/sdk
